item.description: My name is Abod Abbas and I am the President at Schulich Ignite. I am responsible for managing and monitoring the club, alongside being a mentor.
Hello! My name is Anna Lee and I am the VP Finance for Schulich Ignite. I am in my third year of Software Engineering with a minor in Biomedical Engineering.

My name is Fanny Lo and I am the VP of Content Development at Ignite. I am responsible for overseeing the development of any tools our students use, as well as all the lecture content and exercises for our students.
